1309:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * Status indicates whether the transmit buffer is free, or busy transmitting data.
